 a careful discussion about the\nnotion of unique gapped ground states of a particle system on the infinite\nchain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Nov 2021 13:09:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 13:18:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 08:19:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 09:05:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-07"}
