le attention maps for a\nvariety of video-based vision tasks, with possible application to other\nvideo-based vision tasks as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Nov 2021 15:35:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Nov 2021 19:34:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2022 22:14:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
